net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.component

Class AbstractIdentifiedInitializableComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.component.AbstractInitializableComponent
      • net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.component.AbstractIdentifiedInitializableComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Component, DestructableComponent, IdentifiedComponent, InitializableComponent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractIdentifiableInitializableComponent

    public abstract class AbstractIdentifiedInitializableComponent
extends AbstractInitializableComponent
implements IdentifiedComponent
    Simple implementation of InitializableComponent and IdentifiedComponent. Note, this class synchronizes the setId(String) method and, if the component is already initialized this method is treated as no-op.
